{
  "id": "6a0a2f455bc1f296de6b355a",
  "title": "フリーソフィー",
  "created": 1779052360,
  "updated": 1779492446,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0a2f455bc1f296de6b355a",
      "text": "フリーソフィー",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052360,
      "updated": 1779052360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10e65b00000000007b714f",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779492444,
      "updated": 1779492445
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10e65d00000000007b7150",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779492446,
      "updated": 1779492446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2f2f0000000000008bbe",
      "text": " [デライト]の設計哲学の一つ[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052360,
      "updated": 1779052377
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2f410000000000008bc0",
      "text": "  freesophy",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052377,
      "updated": 1779052581
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a300d0000000000008bc5",
      "text": "  「無料哲学」とも",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052581,
      "updated": 1779052656
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2f480000000000008bc1",
      "text": "  [フリーミアム]を超えて",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052385,
      "updated": 1779052481
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2fa80000000000008bc2",
      "text": "   フリーミアム文化を裏切るような [Evernote] の方針が物議をかもしていた時に差別化をはかるため考案",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052481,
      "updated": 1779053269
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2fd00000000000008bc4",
      "text": "   フリーミアムは恣意的なものになりやすいので、デライトでは無料であることを設計哲学に組み込んでしまうことにした",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052521,
      "updated": 1779053241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a30580000000000008bc8",
      "text": "    「無料は品質」である",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052657,
      "updated": 1779053040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a30230000000000008bc6",
      "text": "   詳しいことは『[フリーミアムからフリーソフィーへ https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/E74C-E366?ro]』を読んでもらった方が早いか",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052603,
      "updated": 1779052684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a2faa0000000000008bc3",
      "text": " [造語]としては、フリーミアムとフィロソフィーを同時に連想させつつこの語感の良さ、コンセプトとの調和感、新規性……総合的に最高級のものだと思う",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052483,
      "updated": 1779052991
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a31330000000000008bca",
      "text": "  世界中の[造語家]が嫉妬するレベル",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052876,
      "updated": 1779053289
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a31b30000000000008bcb",
      "text": "  [造語王]の造語能力に震えろ",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779053003,
      "updated": 1779053099
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a30b40000000000008bc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779052749,
      "updated": 1779052749
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a3c7d0000000000627f0c",
      "text": " これが明言されているのは利用者としてありがたい[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779055743,
      "updated": 1779055767
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a3c7f0000000000627f0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779055744,
      "updated": 1779055744
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0aa5a800000000009c1b1d",
      "text": " 面白い[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779082663,
      "updated": 1779082671
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0aa5b100000000009c1b1f",
      "text": "  俺は-ismを使いがちで、ソフィーにつなげるのはなるほどと思った",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779082671,
      "updated": 1779082718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0aa5e300000000009c1b20",
      "text": "  この場合はフリズム/Freeismかな",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779082722,
      "updated": 1779082751
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0abb880000000000d0811d",
      "text": "  だが、[フリーソフィー#6a0a30230000000000008bc6]の文脈だと、フリズムは論外だなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779088265,
      "updated": 1779088275
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0abb950000000000d0811e",
      "text": "  \tそしてフリーソフィーが強いね。同じ状況にいたとして俺もフリーソフィーにたどり着けたかは自信がないし、今もこれより良い造語は浮かばない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779088278,
      "updated": 1779088321
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0aa5a900000000009c1b1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1779082663,
      "updated": 1779082663
    }
  ]
}